# Build-context hygiene for the cortex-agent image.
#
# The build context is the repo root (scripts/Build-AgentImage.ps1 runs
# `docker build <repoRoot>`), but the agent Dockerfile only copies src/,
# lib/memory-mcp/src/MemoryMcp.Core/, and the root Directory.*.props files.
# Without this file Docker shipped the entire tree (~38 GB: artifacts/*.msix,
# .git, and every bin/obj) as context on every build — minutes of transfer
# for nothing. Exclude paths the Dockerfile never references.

.git/
.gitignore
artifacts/
**/bin/
**/obj/
*.msix
*.user
docs/
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
**/TestResults/
